{"tid":1946475,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"台灣終極左膠：滾水燙溝鼠5分鐘致死，都要被人告虐待動物","createTime":"2020-03-27T15:51:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T21:03:17.000Z","uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8a4e94e3f396b53f40d028983267f7b7035a330d","tid":1946475,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"台北市一名呂姓男子2016年10月抓到一隻在廚房亂咬東西的溝鼠，氣得將牠塞進籠子裡浸水，接著再用滾燙的熱水活活澆淋致死，沒想到最後卻挨告虐待動物。台北地院法官認為，該隻老鼠屬於有害的溝鼠，而非有人飼養或管領的寵物，加上用熱水「燙殺」的時間不過5、6分鐘相較短暫，因此不構成虐待致死的要素，判處無罪。<br />\n<br />\n呂男遭指控2016年10月「三度」抓老鼠並用熱水燙死，還將「處刑影片」放到網路上，最後被告發虐待動物並起訴。呂男強調，影片確實是自己拍攝的沒錯，但他只是將影片分成3段上傳，實際上那是同一隻老鼠而非有3隻老鼠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20170909/1007337.htm#ixzz6HuA9c6Ty\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170909%2F1007337.htm%23ixzz6HuA9c6Ty&d=4vI%2Bds9fBAKyPIgWEbj3fgRUsGYs0X8VP9vM6mjQjJM%3D&h=87f9f3ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20170909/1007337.htm#ixzz6HuA9c6Ty</a><br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"525cff42bd9ca2615bda6fd93906f401c782e1ce","tid":1946475,"uid":57677,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"話呢啲係左膠保護動物嘅人,自己試下摸滾水五分鐘先"},{"pid":"376ca135b3938f26fcdff723b984f84228d85b95","tid":1946475,"uid":10612,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:13:32.000Z","msg":"上面有隻啦"},{"pid":"6531289bfd8d9e0df79a26b3f050ea6f2e2a9b82","tid":1946475,"uid":57677,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"525cff42bd9ca2615bda6fd93906f401c782e1ce","tid":1946475,"uid":57677,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"話呢啲係左膠保護動物嘅人,自己試下摸滾水五分鐘先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T16:15:58.000Z","msg":"可以一野扑死/屈頸,親身見過new Zealand breeder/獸醫咁做"},{"pid":"c950f5fdc714d86a219a0096540232e565b751db","tid":1946475,"uid":42767,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTim